---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContactCard from '../components/ContactCard.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About Ice Cap Labs | AI Automation for Service Businesses | Wichita, KS" description="Founded by a former service business owner, Ice Cap Labs builds AI automation systems for HVAC, plumbing, and electrical companies in Wichita, Kansas. Real experience solving real problems.">

  <!-- PAGE TITLE -->
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-title word-reveal">About</h1>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="about-hero" style="background: var(--bg-void);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Who We Are</p>
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal" data-delay="0.05" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem);">AI Automation for Service Businesses</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          Ice Cap Labs builds AI systems that solve the most expensive problems service businesses face: missed calls, lost leads, manual scheduling, and endless admin work.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.85;">
          We specialize in HVAC, plumbing, and electrical companies in Wichita, Kansas — because we understand your business. Not from a case study. From experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOUNDER -->
  <section id="founder" style="background: var(--bg-deep);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">The Founder</p>
      </div>
      <div class="founder-section">
        <img src="/profile-image.jpeg" alt="Maxwell Hinman — Founder of Ice Cap Labs" class="founder-image reveal" />
        <div class="founder-text">
          <h2 class="founder-name reveal">Maxwell Hinman</h2>
          <p class="reveal">
            Before I built AI systems for service businesses, I ran one. I know what it's like when you're on a job site and miss a call. I know the frustration of losing a $2,000 job because you couldn't get to your phone. I know what it feels like to work 12-hour days and still have leads slipping through the cracks.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal">
            That experience is why Ice Cap Labs exists. Most AI agencies pitch you on what's technically possible. I build what actually solves the problems you face every day — because I've faced them too.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal">
            I spent the last two years earning certifications in AI agent architecture and building automation systems from scratch. I've built agents the hard way — 800 lines of custom code, two weeks of debugging, late nights troubleshooting edge cases. That foundation means when I use modern tools, I know exactly how to make them work reliably for your business.
          </p>
          <p class="reveal" style="color: var(--text-primary);">
            Ice Cap Labs is built on a simple idea: AI automation should solve expensive problems for real businesses, not just look impressive in a demo. Every system we build is designed to save you time, capture revenue you're losing, and let you focus on the work that actually matters.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROACH -->
  <section id="approach" style="background: var(--bg-void);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Our Approach</p>
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal" data-delay="0.05">We Know Your Pain Points</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          Missed calls cost you thousands in lost revenue. Manual scheduling eats hours you could spend on billable work. Following up with leads falls through the cracks when you're running between job sites. You're working harder than you should be for the revenue you're bringing in.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
          I've been there. I ran a service business. I know these problems aren't just annoying — they're expensive. And I know the solutions that actually work, because I've built them for myself before I started building them for clients.
        </p>
        <p class="reveal" style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.85;">
          Every system we build starts with one question: "What problem is costing you the most money?" Then we automate it. No fluff, no features you'll never use — just automation that captures revenue and saves time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BELIEVE -->
  <section id="what-we-believe" style="background: var(--bg-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-eyebrow">Our Principles</p>
        <h2 class="section-title word-reveal" data-delay="0.05">What We Believe</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Not slogans. Operating principles behind every decision we make.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.0">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Service Business Expertise</h3>
            <p>Built by someone who ran a service company. I understand your pain points because I've lived them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.05">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/>
              <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>No Overhead Bloat</h3>
            <p>One-person operation means no account managers, no sales teams, no markup. Just expertise at a fair price.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.1">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Sized for Service Businesses</h3>
            <p>No enterprise pricing. No enterprise complexity. Built for 5-50 employee companies that need automation that works.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.15">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>AI That Actually Works</h3>
            <p>We build automations that save real hours. If it doesn't measurably help your business, we don't ship it.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.2">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/>
              <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Strategy First</h3>
            <p>We think about where you're headed, not just what you need today. Technology serves the business model.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="why-item reveal" data-delay="0.25">
          <div class="why-icon">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Full Transparency</h3>
            <p>No black boxes. No mystery retainers. You see everything — clear deliverables, honest timelines.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TILE STRIP -->
  <section id="tile-strip">
    <div class="tile-grid" id="tile-grid"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section id="about-cta" style="background: var(--bg-void);">
    <div class="container">
      <ContactCard
        eyebrow="Ready to Start?"
        title="Let's Talk About Your Business"
        subtitle="No sales pitch. No pressure. Just an honest conversation about what's costing you the most time and money — and how automation can fix it."
        variant="button"
        buttonText="Get Started"
        buttonHref="/contact"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
